        {
            "title": "蘋果據報推觸屏版Macbook Pro　已故「教主」喬布斯曾堅決反對",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"《彭博》指，蘋果最早明年底推出觸屏版Macbook Pro，決定顛覆了已故「教主」喬布斯的立場。(AP)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bq0h33jjVE8lb8yxm_EDFw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/ea0b9083d2430727913ca06db508de15\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">《彭博》指，蘋果最早明年底推出觸屏版Macbook Pro，決定顛覆了已故「教主」喬布斯的立場。(AP)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>據《彭博》報道，蘋果公司(AAPL)計劃於2026年底或2027年初，推出首款配備觸控螢幕的升級版MacBook Pro，有關決定顛覆了已故創辦人「教主」<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:喬布斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/喬布斯\">喬布斯</a>(Steve Jobs)以來堅持的立場。</span></span></span></span></span></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"已故蘋果電腦(Apple)創始人喬布斯(Steve Jobs)。(網上圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"626\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6.aoANjyE.EDhh4gSpEXxQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyNjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/8cd7c75b34c95af46b7940b7825587aa\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">已故蘋果電腦(Apple)創始人喬布斯(Steve Jobs)。(網上圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">最早明年底亮相   <span><span><span><span><span>機身更薄更輕</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>報道透露，該觸控螢幕電腦最早可能在明年底亮相，亦有可能在2027年初推出。新機型的代號為K114和K116，並將擁有更薄更輕的機身，搭載M6系列芯片，亦會採用iPhone及iPad Pro同規格的顯示屏。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-494f652e-4760-324f-95f2-1dd6f8150778-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>另外，在外觀上，蘋果將取消現有機型頂部的「瀏海螢幕」設計，改用穿孔鏡頭方式，使攝影機周圍也能顯示畫面。事實上，早在十多年前不同品牌已開始推出觸屏版筆記型電腦，而2023年就曾傳出蘋果正研發觸屏版MacBook Pro，此舉意味著蘋果將扭轉喬布斯的立場，效仿其他電腦廠商的做法。對此，蘋果發言人拒絕置評。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/蘋果據報推觸屏版macbook-pro-已故-教主-喬布斯曾堅決反對/609508?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/蘋果據報推觸屏版macbook-pro-已故-教主-喬布斯曾堅決反對/609508?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/蘋果據報推觸屏版macbook-pro-已故-教主-喬布斯曾堅決反對/609508?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%8E%A8%E8%A7%B8%E5%B1%8F%E7%89%88macbook-pro-%E5%B7%B2%E6%95%85-%E6%95%99%E4%B8%BB-%E5%96%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF%E6%9B%BE%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-042200241.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 12:35:41",
