        {
            "title": "高市早苗放棄參拜靖國神社 為以後可能參加峰會著想",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 作為在外交政策上立場強硬的政治人物，正在角逐日本首相之位的高市早苗沒有去參拜<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:靖國神社;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/靖國神社\">靖國神社</a>。如果她成功當選，可能會參加多場峰會，其中包括與美國總統川普舉行會晤，而亞洲部分國家認為參拜靖國神社是在美化日本戰爭歷史。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，高市放棄在周五秋季例行大祭首日參拜靖國神社，打破她以往頻繁參拜的慣例。在成功競選自民黨總裁期間，她曾暗示可能會推遲參拜，以免加劇與其他國家的緊張關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這不該成為外交問題，」本月早些時候她被問及是否會繼續參拜靖國神社時表示。「我會在適當時候就祈禱和平妥善做出決定。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fa3ac1c0-db29-37b9-8bc6-e6814b32a458-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當地媒體此前報導稱，高市不會前往靖國神社參拜，她的辦公室也沒有發表官方評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Takaichi Skips Yasukuni Visit Ahead of Possible Summits</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E5%8F%83%E6%8B%9C%E9%9D%96%E5%9C%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%A4%BE-%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E8%91%97%E6%83%B3-084713938.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 17:50:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股午後跌逾500點　金價走強　周大福逆市升逾5%｜恒生指數(持續更新)",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"在中美角力持續的陰霾下，港股半日跌415點，險守25000點關口。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zm1d0oCDndHFtCoNjHKJMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/tl/am730_578/cb4f18da8751e0228c88f3da42c42e19\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">在中美角力持續的陰霾下，港股半日跌415點，險守25000點關口。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span>在中美角力持續的陰霾下，</span></span></span>港股今日(17日)再度承壓。<span><span><span><span><span>恒生指數低開36點後，跌幅擴大至逾400點，半日報25,473點，跌415點，大市成交1,532億元；國企指數9,104點，跌155點；恒生科技指數5,835點，跌168點。</span></span></span></span></span></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"金價再創新高，周大福逆市升逾4%冠藍籌。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BK87THb1LMyTUdoBlPxfLA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/tl/am730_578/e63b5a337f5a9457622cb878bf9fcd80\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">金價再創新高，周大福逆市升逾4%冠藍籌。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>【13:55更新】</strong>恒生指數午後跌幅擴大，跌逾500點，跌穿25,400點，大市成交暫錄1,930億元。金價走強，刺激<span><span><span><span><span>黃金股造好，周大福升5.7%或0.95元，報16.68元，是目前表現最好的</span></span>藍籌。</span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">阿里巴巴跌3  中芯挫逾5%</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>【12:30更新】</strong>88隻藍籌成份股中有75隻下跌，<span><span><span>比亞迪電子(285)跌6.6%，報38.38元，為半日表現最差藍籌；信義光能(968)跌5.4%，報3.48元。</span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4ff00aef-0b1d-37bc-96f5-4cda3e78dae0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>科技股再成跌市</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>主要負累，</span><span>阿里巴巴(9988)跌3.2%，報156.1元；騰訊(700)跌1.5%，報610.5元；京東集團(9618)跌2%，報125.6元；美團(3690)跌2.7%，報96.05元；</span><span>小米(1810)跌2.9%，報46.34元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>晶片股續受壓，中芯(981)跌逾5%，報70.1元；華虹(1347)跌逾3%，報78.6元；ASMPT(522)跌逾4%，報84.6元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>金價突破4,300美元再創新高，黃金股半日個別發展。赤峰黃金(6693)升逾1%，報33.02元；今日公布業績的紫金礦業(2899)跌0.14元，報32.88元；紫金黃金國際(2259)則升近3%，報151.7元；山東黃金(1787)升逾2%，報38.8元；周大福(1928)升逾4%，報16.42元，是半日升幅最大藍籌。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/港股午後跌逾500點-金價走強-周大福逆市升逾5-恒生指數-持續更新-/609526?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/港股午後跌逾500點-金價走強-周大福逆市升逾5-恒生指數-持續更新-/609526?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/港股午後跌逾500點-金價走強-周大福逆市升逾5-恒生指數-持續更新-/609526?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%8D%8A%E6%97%A5%E8%B7%8C415%E9%BB%9E-%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E8%82%A1%E6%B6%AF%E6%B2%BD-%E5%91%A8%E5%A4%A7%E7%A6%8F%E9%80%86%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%87%E9%80%BE4-%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8-%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-045200487.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 14:41:09",
