            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "iPhone Air內地今起預購　僅5分鐘即搶光",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"內地版iPhone Air今日起開始預購，僅5分鐘即售罄。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"656\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9lSzXUcjR1piXbSFG4aheQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/453242e1ae0af32381ab834bfda7106d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">內地版iPhone Air今日起開始預購，僅5分鐘即售罄。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>蘋果<span>iPhone Air</span>今早(17日)9時在內地開始預購，綜合內地媒體報道，官方網站在開售5分鐘已告售罄，其零售店亦已無現貨，送貨交付時間將推遲至一至兩周。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">此前因內地未有eSIM業務延遲發售</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>在京東(9618)平台上，iPhone Air</span></span></span></span></span>多款配色全數顯示缺貨狀態<span><span><span><span><span>，僅雲白色iPhone Air 256GB版本可預約搶購。阿里巴巴(9988)旗下天貓Apple Store官方旗艦店仍可下單，但發貨時間顯示為15日內，</span></span></span></span></span>且嚴格實施每人限購兩部規定。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e84dcfb5-251a-3361-9b0a-e08104429c56-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">iPhone Air取消實體SIM卡槽，改用eSIM設計，<span><span><span><span><span>此前</span></span></span></span></span>因內地未有eSIM手機業務而推遲發售，其後內地3大電訊商中國電信、中國移動和中國聯通開綠燈，開啟eSIM服務。蘋果<span><span><span><span><span>行政總裁庫克(Tim Cook)日前公布，iPhone Air今日開始預購，並於下周三(22日)正式發售。根據蘋果內地官網介紹，iPhone Air售價為7,999元人民幣起，每人限購兩部。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/iphone-air內地今起預購-僅5分鐘即搶光/609544?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/iphone-air內地今起預購-僅5分鐘即搶光/609544?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/iphone-air內地今起預購-僅5分鐘即搶光/609544?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/iphone-air%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E9%A0%90%E8%B3%BC-%E5%83%855%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%8D%B3%E6%90%B6%E5%85%89-053800317.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 14:41:12",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本央行月底會議不遠 行長植田和男仍未排除加息可能性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Kazuo Ueda, governor of the Bank of Japan (BOJ), left, and Atsushi Mimura, Japan's vice finance minister for international affairs, during a news conference in Washington on Oct. 16. Photographer: Takashi Umekawa/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VDDmruGkkzTY.cQKgMY8lQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/18cc6105dfeffaaf5e00dc3448d103c8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Kazuo Ueda, governor of the Bank of Japan (BOJ), left, and Atsushi Mimura, Japan's vice finance minister for international affairs, during a news conference in Washington on Oct. 16. Photographer: Takashi Umekawa/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本央行行長植田和男表示，如果對實現經濟前景的信心增強，央行將繼續收緊政策——這意味著近期加息的大門仍然敞開。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">植田周四在華盛頓參加二十國集團(G20)會議後對記者說道：「我們的立場沒有改變，如果我們對實現經濟前景的信心增強，我們將調整貨幣寬鬆的程度。」 自去年以來，日本央行一直在通過加息和調整資產負債表政策來縮減貨幣刺激措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過植田表示，他可能會等到下次政策委員會會議召開前的最後一刻。他表示，計畫在正在進行的國際會議期間繼續收集信息，並在10月29日至30日的會議前，評估收到的數據。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-110eb794-91fa-323c-9448-57898b5ad2df-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"10月16日，植田和男和日本財務官三村淳在華盛頓舉行的記者會上攝影師：Takashi Umekawa/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t8tp8e2tdL8dX.3jE1hz5g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a114b00e1f0ec2850b1f4a61cfcc3a1d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">10月16日，植田和男和日本財務官三村淳在華盛頓舉行的記者會上攝影師：Takashi Umekawa/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金融市場反映本月底加息的可能性很小。他重申日本央行現有立場，表明即使在國內政治變動和中美貿易緊張局勢升級的情況下，央行仍未排除短期內加息的可能性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當被問及國內政治局勢對政策制定的影響時，植田並沒有具體評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他周四表示，G20成員認為世界經濟總體上具有韌性，但仍面臨較高的不確定性和複雜的挑戰，包括地緣政治和貿易緊張局勢。他表示，金融領導人認為這些問題可能拖累經濟成長，並給金融和價格穩定帶來風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他還指出，關稅的影響顯現緩慢，可能在未來幾個月內浮現。「許多機構和觀察人士仍將其納入展望，或者至少在評估全球和美國經濟時將其視為下行風險。」他說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BOJ’s Ueda Keeps Door Open for Rate Hike as Decision Nears (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Takashi Umekawa.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A0-%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7%E6%A4%8D%E7%94%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%94%B7%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7-001548798.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 08:50:46",
