        {
            "title": "5年期美國公債殖利率跌至2024年10月以來最低水平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/g7TyrE_A7euJPLFFibkNXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f6e876aee79571db2bbad9fb147f34d5\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 5年期美國國債殖利率跌至一年來的最低點，針對美國地區銀行和貿易緊張局勢等疑慮下，投資者轉向安全資產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">殖利率一度下跌3個基點，至3.51%，為2024 年10月初以來的最低水準。此前，2年期美國公債殖利率跌至2022年以來的最低水平，基準10年期公債殖利率跌破4%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtYVwKVpcje0VVSjR.taJA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/224c3db9741e892fc027c2c0b35f6ac5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Van Eck Associates跨資產策略師Anna Wu表示，美國國債今天的上漲是一場避險資產的追逐。隨著信貸相關困境導致不確定性激增，可以說有一些下意識的反應。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-65e9a956-b82d-3224-88a6-d4f8c1b2ce15-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Treasury Five-Year Yield Falls to Lowest Since October 2024</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/5%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%82%B5%E6%AE%96%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B32024%E5%B9%B410%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-035801700.html",
